var book = {
	"name": "Esra",
	"numChapters": 10,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha ka snem ka banyngkong jong u Seiros u syiem ka Persha, khnang ba yn pyndep ïa ka ktien U Trai da ka shyntur u Jeremaïah, U Trai u la pynkhih ïa ka mynsiem u Seiros u syiem ka Persha, kat ban pynlong ka jingpynbna ha ka hima jong u baroh kawei, bad ban buh ïa kata ha kaba thoh de, kaba ong,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Kumne u ong u Seiros u syiem ka Persha, ‘U Trai, U Blei ki bneng, U la ai ha nga ïa ki hima ka pyrthei baroh; bad U la hukum ïa nga ban tei ka ïing ïa U ha Jerusalem, kaba ha Judah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Uno uno ruh uba hapdeng jong phi na ki briew jong U baroh, to U Blei jong u, Un long lem bad u, bad ai un leit kiew sha Jerusalem, kaba ha Judah, bad un tei ïa kata ka ïing U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, (Uta keiñ u long “U Blei”) kaba ha Jerusalem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad jar ïa uba la pynsah, ha kano kano ka jaka ha kaba u la wan wir wanhap, ai ba kita ki trai-shnong ka jaka jong u kin ïarap ïa u da ka rupa, bad da ka ksiar, bad ki mar, bad ki jingri, nalor kata ka jingai sngewbha ïa ka ïing U Blei kaba ha Jerusalem.’ ”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïeng ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki Judah bad ki Benjamin, bad ki lyngdoh, bad ki Lebi, bad baroh kat kiba U Blei u la pynkhih ïa ka mynsiem jong ki ban leit kiew ban tei ïa ka ïing U Trai kaba ha Jerusalem.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad kita baroh kiba la don sawdong ïa ki, ki la kyrshan ïa ki kti jong ki da ki khiew ki pliang rupa, da ka ksiar, da ki mar, bad da ki jingri, bad da kiei kiei kiba kordor, nalor kata baroh ba la ai sngewbha.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u syiem Seiros u la sei noh ïa ki khiew ki pliang jong ka ïing U Trai, ïa kiba u Nebukhadnessar u la lah kit noh na Jerusalem, bad ba u la lah buh ha ka ïing ki blei jong u;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ïa kita keiñ, u Seiros u syiem ka Persha u la sei noh da ka kti u Mithredath u nongsumar jingkynshew, bad u la kheiñ ïa ki ha u Sheshbassar, u rangbah ki Judah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad kane ka long ka jingkheiñ jong ki: laiphew tylli ki pliang ksiar, shi hajar, ki pliang rupa; arphew khyndai, ki tari;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> laiphew tylli ki khuri ksiar; ki khuri rupa kiba kham poh, sawspah shiphew; bad kiwei pat ki khiew ki pliang, shi hajar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki khiew ki pliang baroh bad ksiar bad rupa, ki la long san hajar bad sawspah tylli. Ïa kine baroh u Sheshbassar u la wallam artet, haba ïa kita kiba la ring mraw la ïalam artet na Babilon sha Jerusalem."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te kine ki long ki khun jong kata ka jylla, kiba la leit kiew noh na kata ka jingpynwir jong kita ïa kiba la ring mraw, ïa kiba u Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon u la lah ring mraw sha Babilon, bad kiba la wan phai pat sha Jerusalem bad Judah, uwei uwei baroh sha la ka shnong ka shnong;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> kiba la wan bad u Serubbabel, u Jeshua, u Nehemaïah, u Seraïah, u Rilaïah, u Mordekai, u Bilshan, u Mispar, u Bigbai, u Rehum, u Baanah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki jingkheiñ ki rangbah u paidbah Israel: ki khun u Parosh, ar hajar shispah hynñiewphew ar.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki khun u Shephatiah, laispah hynñiewphew ar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ki khun u Arah, hynñiewspah hynñiewphew san.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ki khun u Pahath-moab, na ki khun u Jeshua bad u Joab, ar hajar phraspah khat-ar.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki khun u Elam, shi hajar arspah sanphew saw.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ki khun u Sattu, khyndaispah sawphew san.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki khun u Sakkai, hynñiewspah hynriewphew.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ki khun u Bani, hynriewspah sawphew ar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ki khun u Bebai, hynriewspah arphew lai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ki khun u Asgad, shi hajar arspah arphew ar.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki khun u Adonikam, hynriewspah hynriewphew hynriew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ki khun u Bigbai, ar hajar sanphew hynriew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ki khun u Adin, sawspah sanphew saw.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ki khun u Ater, ki jong u Hesekaïah, khyndaiphew phra.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ki khun u Besai, laispah arphew lai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ki khun u Ïorah, shispah khat-ar.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ki khun u Hashum, arspah arphew lai.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ki khun Gibbar, khyndaiphew san.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki khun Bethlehem, shispah arphew lai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ki rangbah Netophah, sanphew hynriew.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ki rangbah Anathoth, shispah arphew phra.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki khun Asmabeth, sawphew ar.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki khun Keriatharim, Khephirah, bad Beeroth, hynñiewspah sawphew lai.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki khun Ramah bad Geba, hynriewspah arphew wei.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ki rangbah Mikhmash, shispah arphew ar.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ki rangbah Bethel bad Ai, arspah arphew lai.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ki khun Nebo, sanphew ar.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ki khun Magbish, shispah sanphew hynriew.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ki khun jong uta uwei pat u Elam, shi hajar arspah sanphew saw.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ki khun Harim, laispah arphew.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ki khun Lod, Hadid, bad Ono, hynñiewspah arphew san.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ki khun Jerikho, laispah sawphew san.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ki khun Senaah, lai hajar hynriewspah laiphew.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ki lyngdoh: ki khun u Jedaïah na ka ïing u Jeshua, khyndaispah hynñiewphew lai.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ki khun u Immer, shi hajar sanphew ar.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ki khun u Pashur, shi hajar arspah sawphew hynñiew.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ki khun u Harim, shi hajar khathynñiew.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ki Lebi: ki khun u Jeshua bad u Kadmiel, na ki khun u Hodabiah, hynñiewphew saw.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki nongrwai: ki khun u Asaph, shispah arphew phra.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ki khun ki nongap jingkhang: ki khun u Shallum, ki khun u Ater, ki khun u Talmon, ki khun u Akkub, ki khun u Hatita, ki khun u Shobai, baroh shispah laiphew khyndai.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ki Nethin: ki khun u Siha, ki khun u Hasupha, ki khun u Tabbaoth:",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> ki khun u Keros, ki khun u Siaha, ki khun u Padon;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> ki khun u Lebanah, ki khun u Hagabah, ki khun u Akkub;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> ki khun u Hagab, ki khun u Shamlai, ki khun u Hanan;",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> ki khun u Giddel, ki khun u Gahar, ki khun u Reaïah;",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> ki khun u Resin, ki khun u Nekoda, ki khun u Gassam;",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> ki khun u Ussa, ki khun u Paseah, ki khun u Besai;",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> ki khun u Asnah, ki khun u Meunim, ki khun u Nephisim;",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> ki khun u Bakbuk, ki khun u Hakupha, ki khun u Harhur;",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> ki khun u Basluth, ki khun u Mehida, ki khun u Harsha;",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> ki khun u Barkos, ki khun u Sisera, ki khun u Temah;",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> ki khun u Nesiah, ki khun u Hatipha.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Ki khun ki shakri u Solomon: ki khun u Sotai, ki khun u Hassophereth, ki khun u Peruda;",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> ki khun u Jaalah, ki khun u Darkon, ki khun u Giddel;",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> ki khun u Shephatiah, ki khun u Hattil, ki khun u Pokhereth-hassebaim, ki khun u Ami.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Ki Nethin baroh, bad ki khun ki shakri u Solomon, ki la long laispah khyndaiphew ar.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Kine de ki la long kita kiba la leit kiew na Tel-melah, Tel-harsha, Kherub, Addan, bad Immer: hynrei, kim lah ban pyni ïa ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, lymne ki khun ki ksiew ki jong ki, ba ki long kiba na Israel:",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> ki khun u Delaïah, ki khun u Tobiah, ki khun u Nekoda, hynriewspah sanphew ar.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Na ki khun ki lyngdoh de: ki khun u Habaïah, ki khun u Hakkos, ki khun u Barsillai, uba la shim tnga na ki khun kynthei jong u Barsillai u nong Gilead, bad la khot ïa u ha ka kyrteng jong ki.",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Kine ki la wad ïa la ka rejistor hapdeng kita kiba la kheiñ da ka jingkha pateng, hynrei, ym shym shem ïa ki: namar kata, la kheiñ sang ïa ki, bad la beh noh ïa ki na ka kam lyngdoh.",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> Te u Tirshatha u la ong ha ki, ba kin ym bam na kita kiei kiei ki bakyntang tam ha ban da mih u lyngdoh uba don bad ki Urim bad ki Thummim.",
			"64": "<sup>64</sup> U paidbah baroh lang u la long sawphew ar hajar laispah hynriewphew,",
			"65": "<sup>65</sup> nalor ki shakri shynrang bad ki shakri kynthei jong ki, kita ki la don hynñiew hajar laispah laiphew hynñiew: bad ki la don arspah ki nongrwai shynrang bad ki nongrwai kynthei.",
			"66": "<sup>66</sup> Ki kulai jong ki, ki la long hynñiewspah laiphew hynriew; ki khashor jong ki, arspah sawphew san;",
			"67": "<sup>67</sup> ki ut jong ki, sawspah laiphew san; ki kadda, hynriew hajar hynñiewspah arphew.",
			"68": "<sup>68</sup> Bad na kita ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, haba ki la wan ha ïing U Trai kaba don ha Jerusalem, don kiba la ainguh da la ka mon hi ïa ka ïing U Blei bad pynïeng ïa ka ha la ka jaka.",
			"69": "<sup>69</sup> Ki la ai katba shong ka bor jong ki ha ka jingkynshew ka kam, hynriewphew wei hajar ki darik ksiar, bad san hajar ki maneh rupa, bad shispah riam ki jaiñ lyngdoh.",
			"70": "<sup>70</sup> Kumta, ki lyngdoh, bad ki Lebi, bad katto katne na u paidbah, bad ki nongrwai, bad ki nongap jingkhang, bad ki Nethin, ki la shong ha la ki shnong, bad ki Israel baroh ha la ki shnong."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba la poi u bnai u bahynñiew, bad ki khun Israel ki la don ha kita ki shnong, u paidbah u la ïalum lang baroh kawei sha Jerusalem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki la ïeng u Jeshua u khun u Josadak, bad ki para jong u ki lyngdoh, bad u Serubbabel u khun u Shealtiel, bad ki para jong u, bad ki la tei ïa ka duwan U Blei ki Israel, ban ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang halor jong ka, kumba la thoh ha Ka Hukum u Moses u briew u jong U Blei.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki la buh ïa ka duwan ha la ka jaka; naba ki la sheptieng ïa ki briew kita ki ri: bad ki la ainguh ïa ka jingainguh thang halor jong ka ha U Trai, ïa ki jingainguh thang ba mynstep bad ba la janmiet.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki la rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai Niam Ki Ïingtrep, kumba la thoh, bad ki la ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang kiba ha la ka sngi ha ka jingkheiñ, katba kum ka rukom, katba shong ka kam kawei pa kawei ka sngi;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad hadien kata, ïa ka jingainguh thang kaba borabor, bad ïa ki jong ki 'nai thymmai, bad ki jong Ki Jingkhawai Niam baroh ki bakyntang ba la buh ki jong U Trai, bad ki jong uwei uwei baroh uba la ainguh da la ka mon hi ïa ka jingainguh sngewbha ha U Trai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Naduh ka sngi nyngkong u bnai u bahynñiew ki la sdang ban ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang ha U Trai: hynrei, ïa ka nongrim ka templ ym pat la seng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki la ai sbai ruh ha ki misteri maw, bad ha ki misteri dieng; bad ïa ka jingbam, bad ïa ka jingdih, bad ïa ka umphniang, ha ki nong Sidon, bad ki nong Tyros, ban wallam ïa ki dieng Kedar na Lebanon ha ka duriaw sha Joppa, kat kum ka hukum ba ki la ïoh na u Seiros u syiem ka Persha.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ha ka snem ka ba-ar ka jingwan jong ki sha ka ïing U Blei ha Jerusalem, ha u bnai u ba-ar, u Serubbabel u khun u Shealtiel, bad u Jeshua u khun u Josadak, bad kita kiwei na ki para jong ki, ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, bad kita baroh kat kiba la wan noh na kata ka jingpynwir sha Jerusalem ki la sdang; bad ki la thung ki Lebi, naduh kiba arphew snem bad tam, ban pynïaid ïa ka kam ka ïing U Trai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jeshua bad la ki khun bad la ki para, u Kadmiel bad la ki khun, bad ki khun u Judah, ki la ïeng ryntih baroh, ban pynïaid ïa ki nongtrei ha ka ïing U Blei: ki khun u Henadad, bad la ki khun bad la ki para ki Lebi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki nongtei ki la seng ïa ka nongrim ka templ U Trai, ki la buh ïa ki lyngdoh ba la kup ïa la ki jaiñ bad ki ronsing, bad ïa ki Lebi ki khun u Asaph bad ki shakuriaw, ban ïaroh ïa U Trai, kat kum ka jingbuh u Dabid u syiem ki Israel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la ïarwai phai ktien paralok da kaba ïaroh bad ha kaba ainguh ïa U Trai, ki ïa-ong, “Namar u long u babha, naba ka jingisynei jong u ka neh junom sha ki Israel.” Bad u paidbah baroh u la pyrta da ka jingpyrta bajam, haba ki la ïaroh ïa U Trai namar ba la seng nongrim ïa ka ïing U Trai.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, bun na ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi bad ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, ki tymmen kiba la ïohi ïa ka ïing ka banyngkong, haba la seng nongrim ïa kane ka ïing ha khmat jong ki, ki la ïam da ka ktien bajam; te bun ki la pyrta jam na ka jingkmen:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> katba u paidbah um lah ban pynïapher ïa ka jingsawa ka jingpyrta ka jingkmen na ka jingsawa ka jingïam jong ki briew: naba u paidbah u la pyrta da ka jingpyrta bajam, bad ïa kata ka jingsawa la ïohsngew na sha jngai."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba ki nongshun ki Judah bad ki Benjamin ki la ïohsngew ba kita ki khun ka jingpynwir ki ïatei ïa ka templ ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ynda kumta, ki la ïawan ha u Serubbabel, bad ha ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, bad ki la ong ha ki, “To shah ba ngin ïatei lem bad phi: namar ngi, ngi wad ïa U Blei jong phi, kumba phi, phi wad; bad ngi kñia ïa U naduh ki sngi u Esarhaddon u syiem ka Assyria, uba la wallam artet ïa ngi shane.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u Serubbabel, bad u Jeshua, bad kita ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa ki Israel, ki la ong ha ki, “Phim dei ei ei bad ngi ban tei ïa ka ïing ha U Blei jong ngi; hynrei, ngi hi lang ngin ïatei ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, kumba u syiem Seiros u syiem ka Persha u la hukum ïa ngi.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki briew jong kata ka ri ki la pynduna bor ïa ki kti u paidbah Judah bad ki la pynshitom ïa ki ha kaba tei,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ki la wer ïa ki nongai buit pyrshah ïa ki, ban pyndam noh ïa ka jingthmu jong ki, baroh ki sngi u Seiros u syiem ka Persha, jin haduh ka jingsynshar u Daraïos u syiem ka Persha.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ha ka jingsynshar u Ahasueros, ha kaba sdang ka jingsynshar jong u, ki la thoh ïa ka jingmudui pyrshah ïa ki Judah bad ki Jerusalem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ha ki sngi u Artakserksis, u Bishlam, u Mithredath, u Tabil, bad kita kiwei ki lok jong u, ki la thoh ha u Artakserksis u syiem ka Persha: bad ka jingthoh kata ka shithi la thoh ha ki dak Syria, bad la thoh ha ka ktien Syria.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Rehum u myntri syiem bad u Shimshai nongthoh, ki la thoh ïa ka shithi pyrshah ïa ka Jerusalem ha u Artakserksis u syiem kumne:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Te u Rehum u myntri syiem, bad u Shimshai u nongthoh, bad kita kiwei na ki lok jong ki, ki la thoh; ki Dina, bad ki Apharsath, ki Tarpel, ki Aphar, ki Arkhel, ki Babilon, ki Shushank, ki Deha, ki Elam,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad kita kiwei ki jaid bynriew ïa kiba u Osnappar u bakhraw bad ba-donburom u la wallam na sha shiliang, bad u la pynshong ha ka nongbah Samaria, bad ha kata kawei ka bynta sha shiliang ka wah, bad ei ei bad ei ei.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kane ka long ka kopi na ka shithi kaba ki la phah sha u syiem Artakserksis: “Ki shakri jong me ki briew na sha shiliang ka wah, bad ei ei bad ei ei.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To long ba la tip ha u syiem ba ki Jiw kiba la wan artet na me ki la wan ha ngi sha Jerusalem; ki dang tei ïa ka nongbah kaba shait ïaleh thma bad basniew, bad ki la pyndep ïa ki kynroh, bad ki la shna ïa ki nongrim.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> To long ba la tip ha u syiem te, ba lada yn tei ïa kane ka nongbah, bad ba yn pyndep ïa ki kynroh, kin ym siew ïa ka khajna, ïa ka dustur, lymne ïa ka khrong, bad ha ka bakut kan pynsniew ïa ki syiem.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Mynta te, namar ba ngi bam ïa ka mluh ka ïingsyiem, bad ba kam idei ïa ngi ban khmih ïa ka jingjahburom u syiem, namar kata, ngi la phah ban pyntip skhem ïa u syiem;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ba yn wad ha Ka Kitab Ki Jingkynmaw ki kpa jong me: kumta men shem ha Ka Kitab Ki Jingkynmaw, bad men tip ba kane ka nongbah ka long ka nongbah kaba shait ïaleh thma, bad kaba pynsniew ïa ki syiem bad ïa ki jylla, bad ba ha kane ki la ju pynkhih thma na mynhyndai: namar kata ka daw la pynduh noh ïa kane ka nongbah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ngi pyntip skhem ha u syiem ba, lada yn tei ïa kane ka nongbah, bad ba yn pyndep ïa ki kynroh, da kane men ym don bynta shuh sha shiliang wah.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U syiem u la phah ktien ha u Rehum u myntri syiem, bad ha u Shimshai u nongthoh, bad ha kita kiwei ki lok jong ki, kiba shong ha Samaria, bad ha kata kawei ka bynta sha shiliang ka wah, “Ka jingsuk, bad ei ei bad ei ei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ïa kata ka shithi kaba phi la phah ha ngi la pule shai ha khmat jong nga.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad nga la hukum, bad la wad, bad la shem ba kane ka nongbah na mynhyndai ka ju ïakhih thma ïa ki syiem, bad ba ka jingïaleh pyrshah bad ka jingkhihwin la pynlong ha ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> La ju don ki syiem bakhrawbor ruh halor Jerusalem, kiba la synshar halor baroh kata ka ri sha shiliang ka wah; bad ka khajna, bad ka dustur, bad ka khrong, la ju siew ïa ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ai hukum ban pynpep ïa kine ki briew, bad ba yn ym tei ïa kane ka nongbah, tad ynda ngan ai hukum ma nga.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad sumar ba phin ym leh duna ha kane; balei kan mih ka jingpynsniew ban pynsniew ïa ki syiem?”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba la pule ïa ka kopi ka shithi u syiem Artakserksis ha khmat u Rehum, bad u Shimshai u nongthoh, bad ki lok jong ki, ki la leit kyrkieh sha Jerusalem ha ki Jiw, bad ki la pynpep ïa ki da ka bor bad da ka jingleh-jubor.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ha kata ka por, la pep ka kam ka ïing U Blei kaba ha Jerusalem; bad ka la pep haduh ka snem ka ba-ar ka jingsynshar u Daraïos u syiem ka Persha."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki nongïathuhlypa: u Haggai u nongïathuhlypa, bad u Sekharaïah u khun u Iddo, ki la ïathuhlypa ha ki Jiw kiba don ha Judah bad Jerusalem; ha ka kyrteng U Blei ki Israel ki la ïathuhlypa ïa ki.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, u Serubbabel u khun u Shealtiel, bad u Jeshua u khun u Josadak, ki la ïeng, bad ki la sdang ban tei ïa ka ïing U Blei kaba ha Jerusalem: bad ki nongïathuhlypa U Blei ki la don lem bad ki, ki da ïarap ïa ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ha kata ka por, la wan ha ki u Tatnai, u nongsynshar sha shiliang ka wah, u Shethar-bosnai, bad ki lok jong ki, bad ki la ong kumne ha ki, “Uei ba la hukum ïa phi ban tei ïa kane ka ïing, bad ban pyndep ïa kane ka kynroh?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kumne ngi la ïathuh ha ki, “Kiei ki kyrteng kita ki briew kiba tei ïa kane ka jingtei?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, ka khmat U Blei jong ki ka la long halor ki tymmen basan ki Jiw, bad kim shym la pynpep ïa ki, tad ynda ba yn pynpoi ïa kane ka kam ha u Daraïos, bad ba yn pynphai ktien da ka shithi shaphang kane.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka kopi ka shithi kaba u Tatnai, u nongsynshar sha shiliang ka wah, bad u Shethar-bosnai, bad ki lok jong u ki Apharsak, kiba sha shiliang ka wah, ki la phah sha u Daraïos u syiem:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ki la phah ïa ka shithi sha u, ha kaba la thoh kumne: “Ha u Daraïos u syiem, ka jingsuk baroh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> To long ba la tip ha u syiem, ba ngi la leit sha ka jylla Judah, ha ka ïing U Blei u bakhraw, ïa kaba dang tei da ki maw bakhraw, bad ba buh ki dieng ha ki kynroh, bad kane ka kam ka nang ïaid da kaba minot, bad ka nang roi ha ki kti jong ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ngi la kylli ïa ki tymmen basan, bad ngi la ong ha ki kumne, ‘Uei ba la ai hukum ïa phi ban tei ïa kane ka ïing, bad ban pyndep ïa kane ka kynroh?’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ngi la kylli ïa ki kyrteng jong ki ruh, ban pyntip skhem ha me, ba ngin thoh ïa ki kyrteng kita ki briew kiba long ki rangbah jong ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad kumne ki la ai jubab ïa ngi, ki la ong, ‘Ngi long ki shakri U Blei ka bneng bad ka khyndew, bad ngi tei ïa ka ïing ïa kaba la tei mynta la bun snem, ïa kaba uwei u syiem bakhraw jong ki Israel u la tei bad u la pyndep.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, ynda ba ki kpa jong ngi ki la pynkhih bitar ïa U Blei ka bneng, u la aiti ïa ki ha ka kti u Nebukhadnessar u syiem ka Babilon, u nong Khaldi, uba la pynjot ïa kane ka ïing, bad uba la ring mraw ïa ki briew sha Babilon.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ha ka snem ka banyngkong u Seiros u syiem ka Babilon, u Seiros u syiem u la ai hukum ban tei ïa kane ka ïing U Blei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang ksiar bad rupa ruh ka ïing U Blei, ïa kiba u Nebukhadnessar u la shim noh na ka templ kaba la don ha Jerusalem, bad u la wallam ïa ki ha ka templ Babilon; ïa kita, u Seiros u syiem u la sei noh na ka templ Babilon, bad u la aiti ïa ki ha uwei uba la kyrteng “Sheshbassar”, ïa uba u la thung nongsynshar;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad u la ong ha u, “To shim ïa kine ki khiew ki pliang, khie leit buh ïa ki ha ka templ kaba ha Jerusalem, bad ai ba yn tei ïa ka ïing U Blei ha la ka jaka.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, la wan uta u Sheshbassar, bad u la seng nongrim ïa ka ïing U Blei kaba ha Jerusalem: bad naduh kata ka por haduh mynta dang tei ïa ka, bad ym pat la pyndep.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar kata te, lada ibit u syiem, ai ba yn wad ha ka ïing jingkynshew u syiem, kaba ha Babilon, lada ka long kumta, ba la ai hukum da u Seiros u syiem ban tei ïa kane ka ïing U Blei ha Jerusalem, bad ai ba u syiem un phah ha ngi ïa la ka mon shaphang kane ka kam.”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Daraïos u syiem u la ai hukum, bad la wad ha ka ïing ki kitab, ha kaba la sumar ïa ki jingkynshew ha Babilon.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad la shem ha Akhmetha, ha ka ïingsyiem kaba ha ka jylla Media, ïa ka kot bakli, bad ha ka la thoh kumne ban kynmaw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Ha ka snem ka banyngkong u Seiros u syiem, u Seiros u syiem u la ai hukum; shaphang ka ïing U Blei ha Jerusalem; to tei ïa kata ka ïing, ha ka jaka ha kaba ki kñia ïa ki jingkñia, bad seng skhem ïa ki nongrim jong ka; ka jingjrong jong ka, hynriewphew pruh, bad ka pyngkiang jong ka, hynriewphew pruh;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> bad ki lai kyntiew ki maw bakhraw, bad shi kyntiew ki dieng thymmai: bad ïa ki jinglut yn sei na ka ïing u syiem:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad to ai noh ruh ïa ki khiew ki pliang ksiar bad rupa ka ïing U Blei, ïa kiba u Nebukhadnessar u la shim noh na ka templ kaba ha Jerusalem, bad u la wallam ha Babilon, ban lam pat ha ka templ kaba ha Jerusalem, kawei pa kawei ha la ka jaka, bad men buh ïa ki ha ka ïing U Blei.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Namar kata te, u Tatnai, u nongsynshar sha shiliang ka wah, u Shethar-bosnai, bad ki lok jong phi ki Apharsak, kiba don sha shiliang ka wah, To kynran noh nangta:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> wat ktah ïa ka kam kane ka ïing U Blei; ai ba u nongsynshar ki Jiw bad ki tymmen basan ki Jiw ban tei ïa kane ka ïing U Blei ha la ka jaka.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nalor kane nga ai hukum kaei ba phin leh ïa kine ki tymmen basan ki Jiw ban tei ïa kane ka ïing U Blei: ba na ka spah u syiem, wat na ka khajna sha shiliang ka wah, yn ai noh shisyndon ïa ki jinglut ha kine ki briew, ba yn ym pynpep ïa ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad kata kaba ki donkam, ki masi lyngraw, bad ki langbrot shynrang, bad ki khun langbrot, ïa ki jingainguh thang ha U Blei ka bneng, u Kew, ka mluh, ka Waiñ, bad ka umphniang, katba kum ka ktien ki lyngdoh kiba don ha Jerusalem, yn ai ïa ki man la ka sngi khlem pep:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ba kin ainguh ïa ki jingainguh baiwbih ha U Blei ka bneng, bad ban duwai na ka bynta ka jingim u syiem, bad ki khun jong u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nga la ai hukum ruh ba jar u ban pynkylla ïa kane ka ktien, ba yn law noh ïa ka khung na ka ïing jong u, bad ba yn kyntiew bad sdien ïa u halor jong ka; bad ba yn pynlong lymbher tait ïa ka ïing jong u namar kane:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad uta U Blei uba la pynshong duh ïa la ka kyrteng hangta un pynjot noh ïa ki syiem bad ki briew baroh, ki ban kner noh ïa la ka kti ban pynkylla ïa kane, ban pynjot ïa kane ka ïing U Blei kaba ha Jerusalem. Ma nga u Daraïos nga la hukum; leh ïa ka kumne kumne.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, u Tatnai, u nongsynshar sha shiliang ka wah, u Shethar-bosnai, bad ki lok jong ki, namar ba u Daraïos u syiem u la phah, ki la leh kumta kumne kumne.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad ki tymmen basan ki Jiw ki la tei bad ki la roi, da ka jingïathuhlypa u Haggai u nongïathuhlypa bad u Sekharaïah u khun u Iddo. Bad ki la tei bad ki la pyndep ïa ka, katba kum ka hukum U Blei ki Israel, bad katba kum ka hukum u Seiros, bad u Daraïos, bad u Artakserksis u syiem ka Persha.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ïa kane ka ïing la pyndep ha ka balai sngi u 'nai Adar, ha ka bahynriew snem ka jingsynshar u syiem Daraïos.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki khun Israel, ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, bad kita kiwei ki khun ka jingpynwir, ki la rakhe ïa ka jingpynkyntang ïa kane ka ïing U Blei da kaba kmen.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki la ainguh ha kaba pynkyntang ïa kane ka ïing U Blei, shispah ki masi dab, arspah ki langbrot shynrang, sawspah ki khun langbrot; bad ïa ka jingainguh sait pop na ka bynta ki Israel baroh, khat-ar ki 'lang sohmoh, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ki jaid Israel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ki la buh ïa ki lyngdoh ha la ki bynta bynta, bad ïa ki Lebi ha la ki jingkylliang sngi, ïa ka kam U Blei kaba ha Jerusalem; kumba la thoh ha Ka Kitab u Moses.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki khun ka jingpynwir ki la rakhe ïa Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ha ka bakhatsaw sngi u bnai u banyngkong.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Namar ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ki la lah pynkhuid ïa lade baroh; ki la long ki bakhuid baroh; bad ki la pynïap ïa Ka Jinglait na ka bynta ki khun ka jingpynwir baroh, bad na ka bynta la ki para ki lyngdoh, bad na ka bynta ïa lade.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ki khun Israel, kiba la poi pat na ka jingpynwir, bad baroh kat kiba la pynkyrpang ïa lade sha ki na ka jingijli ki Jentil kata ka ri, ban wad ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, ki la bam,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> bad ki la rakhe ïa Ka Jingkhawai Niam U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat, hynñiew sngi da kaba kmen: namar U Trai u la pynkmen ïa ki, bad u la pynkylla ïa ka dohnud u syiem ka Assyria sha ki, ban pynkhlaiñ ïa ki kti jong ki ha ka kam ka ïing U Blei, U Blei ki Israel."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hadien kine kiei kiei, ha ka jingsynshar u Artakserksis u syiem ka Persha, u Esra u khun u Seraïah, u khun u Asariah, u khun u Hilkiah,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u khun u Shallum, u khun u Sadok, u khun u Ahitub,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> u khun u Amariah, u khun u Asaraïah, u khun u Meraïoth,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> u khun u Serahiah, u khun u Ussi, u khun u Bukki,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> u khun u Abishua, u khun u Phinehas, u khun u Eleasar, u khun u Aaron u rangbah lyngdoh:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> une u Esra la leit kiew na Babilon; bad u la long u nongthoh uba nang ha Ka Hukum u Moses, ïa kaba U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, U la ai: bad u syiem u la ai ha u ïa ka jingkyrpad jong u baroh, kat kumba ka kti U Trai U Blei jong u kaba halor jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad don kiba la leit kiew na ki khun Israel, bad na ki lyngdoh, bad na ki Lebi, bad na ki nongrwai, bad na ki nongap jingkhang, bad na ki Nethin, sha Jerusalem, ha ka snem ka bahynñiew u Artakserksis u syiem.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki la poi ha Jerusalem ha u bnai u basan, ha ka snem ka bahynñiew u syiem.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar ha ka sngi nyngkong u bnai u banyngkong u la mih ban leit kiew na Babilon, bad ha ka sngi nyngkong u bnai u basan u la poi ha Jerusalem, kat kumba ka kti babha U Blei jong u kaba halor jong u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar u Esra u la buh ha la ka dohnud ban wad ïa ka hukum U Trai, bad ban leh ïa ka, bad ban hikai ha Israel ïa ki aiñ bad ïa ki jingbishar.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kane ka long ka kopi ka shithi kaba u Artakserksis u syiem u la ai ha u Esra lyngdoh u nongthoh, u nongthoh ki ktien ki hukum U Trai, bad ki aiñ jong U ha ki Israel.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “U Artakserksis, u syiem ki syiem, ha u Esra u lyngdoh, u nongthoh Ka Hukum U Blei ka bneng, ka jingjanai bad ei ei bad ei ei.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nga ai hukum, ba baroh na u paidlang Israel, bad ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi jong ki, ha ka hima jong nga, kiba mon hi ban leit sha Jerusalem, kin leit bad me.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar ba la phah ïa me da u syiem bad ki hynñiew ngut ki myntri jong u, ban tohkit shaphang ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem, katba kum Ka Hukum U Blei jong me kaba don ha ka kti jong me;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ban rah ïa ka rupa bad ïa ka ksiar, kiba u syiem bad ki myntri jong u ki la ainguh sngewbha ha U Blei ki Israel, uba shong ha Jerusalem,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> bad ïa ka rupa bad ïa ka ksiar baroh kiba men ïoh ha ka jylla Babilon baroh kawei, bad ka jingainguh sngewbha u paidlang, bad ka jong ki lyngdoh, kiba ainguh sngewbha ïa ka ïing U Blei jong ki kaba ha Jerusalem;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> namar kata, men thied kumne kumne da kine ki sbai ïa ki masi dab, ki langbrot shynrang, ki khun langbrot, bad ka jingainguh bam jong ki bad ki jingainguh dih jong ki, bad men ainguh ïa ki halor ka duwan ka ïing U Blei jong phi kaba ha Jerusalem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ïa kaei kaei kaba ibit ma me bad ki para jong me ban leh bad kaba sah na ka rupa bad ka ksiar, ïa kata leh phi katba kum ka mon U Blei jong phi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang kiba la ai ha me ïa ka kam ka ïing U Blei jong me, to aiti ha khmat U Blei ka Jerusalem.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ïa kaei kaei ba dang donkam shuh ïa ka ïing U Blei jong me, ïa kaba me donkam ban ai, to ai ïa ka na ïing jingkynshew u syiem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Bad nga, wat ma nga u Artakserksis u syiem, nga ai hukum ha ki nongsumar jingkynshew baroh kiba sha shiliang ka wah, ba ïa kaei kaei ba u Esra lyngdoh, u nongthoh Ka Hukum U Blei ka bneng, un pan na phi, ïa kata to leh kumne kumne,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> haduh shispah ki talent rupa, bad shispah byrni u Kew, bad shispah bath ka Waiñ, bad shispah bath ka umphniang, bad ka mluh khlem da thew.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ïa kaei kaei ba la hukum da U Blei ka bneng, leh kumta biang ïa ka ïing U Blei ka bneng: namar ban lei yn long ka jingbitar ïa ka hima u syiem bad ki khun jong u?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ngi pyntip skhem ruh ïa phi, ba shaphang uno uno na ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, ki nongrwai, ki nongap jingkhang, ki Nethin, lane ki shakri ka ïing U Blei, ba kam dei ban buh khajna, ka dustur, lymne ka khrong, halor jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Bad me, u Esra, katba kum ka jingstad U Blei jong me kaba don ha ka kti jong me, to thung ïa ki majistor bad ïa ki nongbishar, ki ban bishar ïa u paidlang baroh uba don sha shiliang ka wah, baroh kat kiba nang ïa ki hukum U Blei jong me; bad to hikai ïa uta u bymnang ïa ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad jar u bymleh ïa ka hukum U Blei jong me, bad ïa ka hukum u syiem, to pyndep ïa ka jingbishar halor jong u kumne kumne, la u dei ban ïap, lane ban beh shnong, lane ban kurup mar, lane ban set byndi.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “To long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong ngi, uba la buh kat kane ha ka dohnud u syiem, ban pynitynnad ïa ka ïing U Trai kaba ha Jerusalem;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad u la ai ïa ka jingisynei ha nga ha khmat u syiem, bad ki myntri jong u, bad ha khmat ki rangbah badonbor jong u syiem baroh. Bad la pynkhlaiñ ïa nga katba kum ka kti U Trai U Blei jong nga kaba halor jong nga, bad nga la ïalum lang ïa ki rangbah na ki Israel ban leit kiew bad nga.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Kine te ki long ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, bad kane ka long ka jingkha pateng jong kita kiba la leit kiew bad nga na Babilon, ha ka jingsynshar u Artakserksis u syiem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ki khun u Phinehas, u Gershom; na ki khun u Ithamar, u Daniel; na ki khun u Dabid, u Hattush.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ki khun u Shekaniah; na ki khun u Parosh, u Sekharaïah: bad lem bad u la kheiñ katba kum ka jingkha pateng la pateng, shispah sanphew ki shynrang.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ki khun u Pahath-moab, u Eliehoenai u khun u Serahiah; bad lem bad u, arspah ngut ki shynrang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ki khun u Shekaniah, u khun u Jahasiel; bad lem bad u, laispah ngut ki shynrang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad na ki khun u Adin, u Ebed u khun u Jonathan; bad lem bad u, sanphew ngut ki shynrang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad na ki khun u Elam, u Jeshaïah u khun u Athaliah; bad lem bad u, hynñiewphew ngut ki shynrang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad na ki khun u Shephatiah, u Sebadiah u khun u Mikhael; bad lem bad u, phraphew ngut ki shynrang.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ki khun u Joab, u Obadaïah u khun u Jehiel; bad lem bad u, arspah khatphra ngut ki shynrang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad na ki khun u Shelomith, u khun u Josiphiah; bad lem bad u, shispah hynriewphew ngut ki shynrang.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad na ki khun u Bebai, u Sekharaïah u khun u Bebai; bad lem bad u, arphew phra ngut ki shynrang.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad na ki khun u Asgad, u Johanan u khun u Hakkatan; bad lem bad u, shispah shiphew ngut ki shynrang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad na ki khun u Adonikam, ki bakhatduh; bad kine ki long ki kyrteng jong ki: u Eliphelet, u Jewel, bad u Shemaïah, bad lem bad ki, hynriewphew ngut ki shynrang,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad na ki khun u Bigbai, u Uthai bad u Sabbud; bad lem bad ki, hynñiewphew ngut ki shynrang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad nga la lum lang ïa ki sha kata ka wah kaba tuid sha Ahaba; bad hangta ngi la ïashong dara lai sngi; bad nga la jngoh ïa u paidlang, bad ïa ki lyngdoh, bad nga la shem ba ym don uwei na ki khun u Lebi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, nga la phah khot ïa u Elieser, ïa u Ariel, ïa u Shemaïah, bad ïa u Elnathan, bad ïa u Jarib, bad ïa u Elnathan, bad ïa u Nathan, bad ïa u Sekharaïah, bad ïa u Meshullam, ki rangbah; ïa u Joïarib ruh, bad ïa u Elnathan, kiba long ki nonghikai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad nga la phah noh ïa ki sha u Iddo u rangbah ka jaka Kasiphia; bad nga la ïathuh ha ki, ïa kaei ba kin ong ha u Iddo, bad ki para jong u ki Nethin, ha ka jaka Kasiphia, ba kin wallam shakri ha ngi ïa ka ïing U Blei jong ngi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad katba kum ka kti babha U Blei jong ngi kaba halor jong ngi, ki la wallam ha ngi ïa u briew bastad buit, na ki khun u Mahli, u khun u Lebi, u khun u Israel; bad ïa u Sherebiah, bad ki khun jong u bad ki para jong u, khatphra ngut;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ïa u Hashabiah, bad lem bad u, u Jeshaïah na ki khun u Merari, ki para jong u bad ki khun jong ki, arphew ngut;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad na ki Nethin, ïa kiba u Dabid bad ki rangbah ki la ai ïa ka jingshakri ki Lebi, arspah arphew ngut ki Nethin: ïa kine baroh la ïathuh kyrteng.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, nga la pynbna ïa ka jingshah jingit hangta, harud kata ka wah Ahaba, ba ngin pynrit ïa lade ha khmat U Blei jong ngi, ban wad na u ïa ka lynti ba-beit, ïa lade, bad ïa ki khun jong ngi, bad ïa ka spah jong ngi baroh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar nga la sngewlehrain ban pan na u syiem, ïa ka kynhun shipai bad ki nongshong kulai ban ïarap ïa ngi pyrshah ïa ki nongshun ha lynti: namar ngi la lah kren ha u syiem, da kaba ong, “Ka kti U Blei jong ngi ka long halor kita baroh kiba wad ïa u, ïa ka ban pynbha; hynrei, ka bor jong u bad ka jingbitar jong u ka pyrshah ïa kita baroh kiba kyntait ïa u.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, ngi la shah jingit bad ngi la wad ïa U Blei jong ngi na ka bynta kane: bad u la shahshkor ïa ngi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te nga la buh kyrpang khat-ar ngut na ki rangbah ki lyngdoh, u Sherebiah, u Hashabiah bad shiphew ngut na ki para jong ki lem bad ki,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad nga la thew ha ki, ïa ka rupa, bad ïa ka ksiar, bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang, ka jingainguh ïa ka ïing U Blei jong ngi, ïa kiba u syiem, bad ki myntri jong u, bad ki rangbah jong u, bad ki Israel baroh kiba don hangta, ki la lah ainguh:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> nga la thew ha ki kti jong ki, hynriewspah sanphew talent, ka rupa; bad ki khiew ki pliang rupa, shispah talent; ka ksiar, shispah talent;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad arphew, ki khuri ksiar, kiba long shi hajar darik; bad ar tylli ki khiew tama banylla baphyrnai, bakordor kat ka ksiar.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad nga la ong ha ki, “Phi long ki bakyntang ha U Trai, bad ki khiew ki pliang ki long ki bakyntang; bad ka rupa bad ka ksiar ki long ki jingainguh sngewbha ha U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong phi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> To sharai, bad to sumar ïa ki, tad ynda phin thew ïa ki ha khmat ki rangbah ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, bad ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa ki Israel, ha Jerusalem, ha ki kamra ka ïing U Trai.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumta, ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi ki la pdiang ïa ka jingthew ka rupa bad ka ksiar, bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang, ban wallam ïa ki sha Jerusalem ha ka ïing U Blei jong ngi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, ngi la mih noh na kata ka wah Ahaba ha ka bakhat-ar sngi u bnai u banyngkong, ban leit sha Jerusalem: bad ka kti U Blei jong ngi ka la long halor jong ngi, bad u la ri pynim ïa ngi na ka kti u nongshun bad uba ap thap ha ka lynti.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ngi la poi sha Jerusalem, bad ngi la shong hangta, lai sngi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad ha ka basaw sngi, la thew ïa ka rupa bad ïa ka ksiar bad ïa ki khiew ki pliang ha ka ïing U Blei jong ngi ha ka kti u Meremoth u khun u Uriah lyngdoh; bad lem ba u, u la don u Eleasar u khun u Phinehas; bad lem bad ki, u la don u Josabad u khun u Jeshua, bad u Noadiah u khun u Binnui, ki Lebi:",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> baroh katba kum ka jingkheiñ bad ka jingthew: bad ïa ka jingthew baroh la thoh ha kata ka por.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ki khun ka jingpynwir, kiba la wan noh na ka jingpynwir, ki la ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang ha U Blei ki Israel, khat-ar tylli, ki masi dab na ka bynta ki Israel baroh; khyndaiphew hynriew, ki langbrot shynrang; hynñiewphew hynñiew, ki khun langbrot; khat-ar, ki 'lang sohmoh ïa ka jingainguh sait pop: kane baroh ka la long ka jingainguh thang ha U Trai.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad ki la aiti ïa ki hukum u syiem ha ki satrap u syiem, bad ha ki nongsynshar sha shiliang ka wah: bad ki la ïarap ïa u paidbah bad ïa ka ïing U Blei."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda la pyndep ïa kine kiei kiei, ki rangbah ki la ïashur jan sha nga, ki ïa-ong, “U paidbah ki Israel, bad ki lyngdoh bad ki Lebi, kim shym la pynkyrpang ïa lade na ki briew kine ki ri, ki da leh katba kum ka jingijli jong ki, ki jong ki Kanaan, ki Hit, ki Peris, ki Jebus, ki Ammon, ki Moab, ki Ijipt, bad ki Amor.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar ki la shim na ki khun kynthei jong ki ïa lade bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong ki; ba kumta u symbai bakyntang u la pynïakhleh ïa lade bad ki briew kita ki ri: ho-oid keiñ, ka kti ki rangbah bad ki nongsynshar ka la long ka banyngkong ha kane ka jingpalat.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba nga la ïohsngew ïa kane, nga la kad ïa la ka jaiñkup bad ïa la ka jingphong, bad nga la phut noh ïa la u 'ñiuh khlieh bad la u 'ñiuh tmoh, bad nga la shong lyngngoh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hangta la ïalum lang ha nga baroh kat uba khynñiuh ha ki ktien U Blei ki Israel, namar ka jingpalat jong kita kiba na ka jingpynwir; bad nga la shong lyngngoh haduh ka jingkñia la janmiet.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ha ka jingkñia la janmiet nga la ïeng joit na la ka jingshah jingit, ba la kad noh la ka jaiñkup bad la ka jingphong; bad nga la hap dem ha la ki khohsiew, bad nga la pyiar noh ïa la ki kti ha U Trai U Blei jong nga;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad nga la ong, “A U Blei jong nga, nga sngewlehrain bad nga saw kyr-ang ban khmied la ka khmat sha me, U Blei jong nga: namar ki jingleh bymman jong ngi ki la man bun shaneng ka khlieh jong ngi, bad ka jingtei pop jong ngi ka la san haduh ki bneng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Naduh ki sngi ki kpa jong ngi haduh kane ka sngi, ngi la long ha ka jingrem bakhraw; bad namar ki jingleh bymman jong ngi, la aiti noh ïa ngi, ïa ki syiem jong ngi, bad ïa ki lyngdoh jong ngi, ha ki kti ki syiem kita ki ri, ha ka waitlam, ha ka jingpynwir, bad ha ka jinglute, bad ha ka jinglehrain ka khmat, kumba ka long ha kane ka sngi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad mynta, ïa kaba khyndiat ka por, la wan ka jingaiei na U Trai U Blei jong ngi, ban iehnoh ha ngi khyndiat kiba sah ban ïohlait, bad ban ai ha ngi ïa u prek ha ka jaka bakhuid jong U, ba U Blei jong ngi un pynshai ïa ki khmat jong ngi, bad ban ai khyndiat ka jingshongthait ha ngi ha ka jinglongmraw jong ngi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar ngi long ki mraw: pynban, U Blei jong ngi um shym la iehnoh ïa ngi ha ka jinglongmraw jong ngi, hynrei, u la ai ïa ka jingisynei ha ngi ha khmat ki syiem ka Persha, ban ai ka jingshongthait ha ngi, ban pynïeng ïa ka ïing U Blei jong ngi, bad ban shna pat ïa ka jingjot jong ka bad ban ai ka kynroh ha ngi ha Judah bad ha Jerusalem.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> “Bad mynta, A U Blei jong ngi, kaei ngin ong hadien kane pat? namar ngi la kyntait ïa ki hukum jong me,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ïa kiba me la hukum da ki shakri jong me ki nongïathuhlypa, ki ïa-ong, ‘Kata ka ri, ha kaba phi leit ban ïoh ïa ka, ka long ka ri bymkhuid da ka jingbymkhuid ki briew kita ki ri, da ka jingijli jong ki kiba la pyndap ïa ka na kut sha kut da ka jingtngit jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Namar kata te, wat ai ïa ki khun kynthei jong phi ha ki khun shynrang jong ki, lymne wat shim ïa ki khun kynthei jong ki ha ki khun shynrang jong phi, lymne wat wad ïa ka jingsuk jong ki lymne ïa ka jingmanbha jong ki lano lano ruh: ba phin long ki bakhlaiñ, bad phin bam ïa ka jingbha ka ri, bad ba phin iehnoh ïa ka kum ka jingïoh pateng ha ki khun jong phi junom la junom.’",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad hadien baroh kaba la jia ha ngi namar ki jinglehsniew jong ngi, bad namar ka jingrem bakhraw jong ngi, ngi ïohi ba me U Blei jong ngi me la pynshitom ïa ngi kham duna ban ïa kaba ki pop jong ngi ki dawa, bad ba me la ai ha ngi katne kiba sah,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> hato ngin pynkheiñ shuh ïa ki hukum jong me, bad ngin shongkurim bad kine ki briew kiba leh ïa kine ki jingijli? men ym bitar bad ngi tad ynda me la lah bam duh ïa ngi, ba kumta ba ym don ba sah shuh, lymne uwei ruh ban ïohlait?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, me long u bahok; namar la pynsah ïa ngi khyndiat kiba la ïohlait, kumba ka long ha kane ka sngi: ha khmih, ngi long ha khmat jong me ha ka jingrem jong ngi; namar ym don uba lah ban ïeng ha khmat jong me namar kane.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te katba u Esra u duwai, bad u phla, da kaba ïam bad pyndem ngon ïa lade ha khmat ka ïing U Blei, la ïalum lang ha u na ki Israel u paidlang bakhraw eh ki shynrang bad ki kynthei bad ki khynnah: namar u paidlang u la ïam shikatdei eh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Shekhaniah u khun u Jehiel, uwei na ki khun u Elam, u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u Esra, “Ngi la leh pop ïa U Blei jong ngi, bad ngi la shongkurim ïa ki kynthei nongwei kiba na ki briew kane ka ri: pynban, mynta, don ka jingkyrmen ïa ki Israel shaphang kane.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar kata te, ai ba ngin thaw jutang bad U Blei jong ngi ban iehnoh noh ïa kita ki tnga baroh, bad kat kiba la kha na ki, katba kum ka jingsneng u kynrad jong nga, bad ka jong kita kiba khynñiuh ha ka hukum U Blei jong ngi; bad ai ba yn leh ïa kata katba kum ka hukum.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> To ïeng; namar kane ka kam ka dei ka jong me, bad ngi long lem bad me, long u bashlur bha, bad leh ïa kane.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Esra u la ïeng, bad u la pynsmai ïa kiba kham rangbah na ki lyngdoh, ïa ki Lebi, bad ïa ki Israel baroh, ba kin leh katba kum kane ka ktien, kumta ki la smai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u Esra u la ïeng na sha khmat ka ïing U Blei, bad u la leit bsut ha ka kamra u Jehohanan u khun u Eliashib; bad haba u la poi hangta, um shym la bam kpu, lymne dih um: naba u la ïam namar ka jingpalat jong kita kiba na ka jingpynwir.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad ki la pynbna lyngba ka Judah bad ka Jerusalem baroh ha ki khun ka jingpynwir, ban ïalum lang ha Jerusalem;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad jar u bym shym la wan hapdeng lai sngi, katba kum ka jingsneng ki rangbah bad ki tymmen basan, yn kurup noh ïa ka spah jong u baroh, bad ba yn pynïakhlad noh ïa u hi na u paidlang ka jingpynwir.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki rangbah Judah bad Benjamin baroh ki la ïalum lang ha Jerusalem hapdeng lai sngi; ka la long ha u bnai u bakhyndai, ha ka ba-arphew sngi na uta u bnai: bad u paidbah baroh u la shong ha kata ka bakylluid ka jaka ha khmat ka ïing U Blei, ki da khynñiuh shaphang kane ka kam, bad namar u 'lap bah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Esra lyngdoh u la ïeng, bad u la ong ha ki, “Phi la leh pop, bad phi la shongkurim ïa ki kynthei nongwei, ban pynkhraw ïa ka jingrem ki Israel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata te, to phla ha U Trai, U Blei ki kpa jong phi, bad leh ïa ka mon jong u: bad pynïakhlad noh ïa lade na ki briew kane ka ri, bad na ki kynthei nongwei.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u paidlang baroh u la ïathuh bad u la ong da ka ktien bajam, “Kumba me la ong shaphang jong ngi, kumta dei ba ngin leh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ki briew ki long shibun, bad ka long ka por 'lap bah, ngim lah ban ïeng habar, lymne kane kam long ka kam shi sngi ar sngi: namar ngi la leh pop shikatdei eh ha kane ka kam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> To ai te ba yn thung ïa ki rangbah jong ngi na ka bynta u paidbah baroh, bad to ai ba kita baroh kiba don ha ki shnong jong ngi kiba la shongkurim ïa ki kynthei nongwei kin wan ha ki por ba la buh, bad lem bad ki, ki tymmen basan kawei pa kawei ka shnong bad ki nongbishar jong ka, tad ynda yn pynphai noh ïa ka jingbitar ba-itieng U Blei jong ngi na ngi, haduh ban da pyndep noh ïa kane ka kam.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Tang u Jonathan u khun u Asahel bad u Jahseïah u khun u Tikbah ki la ïeng pyrshah ïa kane: bad u Meshullam bad u Shabbethai u Lebi ki la ïarap ïa ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki khun ka jingpynwir ki la leh kumta. Bad u Esra lyngdoh, bad katto katne ki rangbah ki ïing ki kpa, katba kum ki ïing ki kpa jong ki, bad kita baroh da la ki kyrteng, la buh kyrpang; bad ki la shong ha ka sngi nyngkong na u bnai u bashiphew ban kylli shaphang kane ka kam.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki la pyndep noh bad kita ki briew baroh kiba la shongkurim ïa ki kynthei nongwei ha ka sngi nyngkong u bnai u banyngkong.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad hapdeng ki khun ki lyngdoh, la shem kiba la shongkurim ïa ki kynthei nongwei: na ki khun u Jeshua, u khun u Josadak, bad ki para jong u, u Maaseïah, bad u Elieser, bad u Jarib, bad u Gedaliah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ki la ai ïa la ka kti ba kin iehnoh noh ïa la ki tnga; bad ba ki da sngewrem, ki la ainguh ïa u langbrot na ka kynhun na ka bynta la ka jingrem.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad na ki khun u Immer: u Hanani bad u Sebadiah.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad na ki khun u Harim: u Maaseïah, bad u Elijah, bad u Shemaïah, bad u Jehiel, bad u Ussiah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad na ki khun u Pashur: u Elioenai, u Maaseïah, u Ishmael, u Nethanel, u Josabad, bad u Elasah.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad na ki Lebi: u Josabad, bad u Shimei, bad u Keliah (uta u long u Kelita), u Pethahiah, u Judah, bad u Elieser.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad na ki nongrwai: u Eliashib; bad na ki nongap jingkhang: u Shallum, bad u Telem, bad u Uri.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad na ki Israel: na ki khun u Parosh: u Ramiah, bad u Issiah, bad u Malkhijah, bad u Mijamin, bad u Eleasar, bad u Malkhijah, bad u Benaïah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad na ki khun u Elam: u Mattaniah, u Sekharaïah, bad u Jehiel, bad u Abdi, bad u Jeremoth, bad u Elijah.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad na ki khun u Sattu: u Elioenai, u Eliashib, u Mattaniah, bad u Jeremoth, bad u Sabad, bad u Asisa.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad na ki khun u Bebai: u Jehohanan, u Hananiah, u Sabbai, u Athlai.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad na ki khun u Bani: u Meshullam, u Mallukh bad u Adiah, u Jashub, bad u Sheal, u Jeremoth.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Bad na ki khun u Pahath-moab: u Adna, bad u Khelal, u Benaïah, u Maaseïah, u Mattaniah, u Besalil, bad u Binnui, bad u Manasseh.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad na ki khun u Harim: u Elieser, u Isshijah, u Malkhijah, u Shemaïah, u Shimeon;",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> u Benjamin, u Mallukh, u Shemariah.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na ki khun u Hashum: u Mattenai, Mattattah, u Sabad, u Eliphelet, u Jeremai, u Manasseh, u Shimei.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ki khun u Bani: u Maadai, u Amram, u Uel;",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> u Benaïah, u Bedaïah, u Kheluhi;",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> u Baniah, u Meremoth, u Eliashib;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> u Mattaniah, u Mattenai, bad u Jaasu;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> bad u Bani, bad u Binnui, u Shimei;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> bad u Shelemiah, bad u Nathan bad u Adiah;",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> u Makhnadebai, u Shashai, u Sharai;",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> u Asarel, bad u Shelemiah, Shemariah;",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> u Shallum, u Amariah, u Joseph.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Na ki khun u Nebo: u Jeiel, u Mattithiah, u Sabad, u Sebina, u Iddo, bad u Joel, u Benaïah.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Kine baroh ki la shim ki tnga nongwei; bad don na ki kiba don ki tnga na kiba ki la ïoh khun."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;